que han actuado.

select a.nombre, ft.title
from actor a
join pelicula_actor as pa
	on a.id_actor = pa.id_actor
join pelicula as p
	on p.id_pelicula = pa.id_pelicula
join film_text ft
	on ft.film_id = p.id_pelicula;
